#: base/models/organizer.py:457
msgid "Video: Can create channels"
msgstr "វីដេអូ៖ អាចបង្កើតឆានែល"

#: base/models/organizer.py:458
msgid "Allows creating chat/video channels inside Eventyay Video."
msgstr "អនុញ្ញាតឱ្យបង្កើតឆានែលជជែក/វីដេអូ នៅក្នុង Eventyay Video។"

#: base/models/organizer.py:462
