msgstr "កាតអំណោយនេះមានសុពលភាពរហូតដល់ %(expiry)s។"

#: presale/templates/pretixpresale/event/order.html:173
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A refund of %(amount)s has been sent to you. Depending on the payment "
